{
  "stem": "22685.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when the war broke out between Russia and Germany, they started to-- they decided to use the, the Polish people as an army.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So [NON-ENGLISH], who was a famous communist in Poland, she organized a, a, a Polish Army.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So first of all, they freed all the Polish citizens from the camps.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The other army was organized by Anders.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, this was a Polish general.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Begin, as a matter of fact, went with Anders's Army to Palestine at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was-- he got-- he asked legally because Begin was old-time gentleman, that you don't go away from an army, even if you hate that army, or that army was only used for a certain purposes.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He had to have a legal dismissal.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he got it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so those-- many of those people who came out of the camps, since they were familiar with working in forests, came back to Russia on the Volga and the Don where I lived.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they worked again in the camp in the forests.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he told me, there are several Polish people working in these forests.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If I will go among them, you will be one of them-- to protect me.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then he said, in the forest are two jobs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One is to cut the wood-- the trees, which used to be maybe meant as a compliment, or to work on a horse.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Am I familiar with horses?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, of course, I'm-- I had two horses home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't see-- I, I-- the only horse I saw is in the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And but I knew it's a simpler-- it is going to be an easier job.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
